Ning%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20X%20featuring%20a%20man%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20US%20importer.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20the%20man%20addresses%20the%20American%20public%2C%20especially%20Trump%20supporters%2C%20warning%20that%20ordinary%20citizens%20-not%20foreign%20countries-%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20Trump's%20aggressive%20trade%20policies%2C%20which%20would%20hike%20the%20prices%20of%20imported%20items%20and%20burden%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EForeign%20countries%20pay%20the%20tariffs%3F%20No%E2%80%94US%20businesses%20pay%2C%20then%20pass%20costs%20to%20you.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTariffs%20don't%20bring%20manufacturing%20back.%20They're%20just%20a%20tax%20on%20Americans.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FiOw3IrFpiQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FiOw3IrFpiQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mao%20Ning%20%E6%AF%9B%E5%AE%81%20(%40SpoxCHN_MaoNing)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpoxCHN_MaoNing%2Fstatus%2F1911206346965602406%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2012%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20countries%20pay%20the%20tariffs%3F%20No%20-%20US%20businesses%20pay%2C%20then%20pass%20costs%20to%20you.%20Tariffs%20don't%20bring%20manufacturing%20back.%20They're%20just%20a%20tax%20on%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20Mao%20captioned%20the%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS-China%20Trade%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20comes%20amid%20escalating%20economic%20tension%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20imposed%20hefty%20taxes%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20on%20Wednesday%20increased%20the%20stakes%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20that%20threatens%20to%20upend%20global%20supply%20chains%20by%20raising