0Bano%2C%20said%20that%20her%20sister-in-law%20did%20not%20like%20her%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20that%20she%20pushed%20him.%20She%20did%20not%20like%20our%20brother%20and%20often%20fought%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20mother%2C%20Qureesha%20Bano%20-%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20society%20as%20the%20couple%20-%20said%20they%20used%20to%20fight%20over%20Shanno%20talking%20to%20someone%20for%20hours%20since%20the%20past%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20%26quot%3BThey%20used%20to%20fight%20every%20day%20over%20this.%20She%20has%20even%20run%20away%20from%20home%20a%20couple%20of%20times.%20Even%20then%2C%20my%20son%20got%20her%20back.%20She%20used%20to%20beat%20my%20son%20too...Because%20of%20her%2C%20my%20son%20is%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanno%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20allegations%2C%20saying%20her%20husband%20jumped%20from%20the%20roof.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20Dilshad%20was%20an%20alcoholic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20came%20home%20drunk%20yesterday%20and%20jumped%20from%20the%20roof.%20He%20used%20to%20come%20home%20drunk%20every%20day...My%20mother-in-law%20is%20making%20false%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20have%20been%20married%20for%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20for%20eight%20years%20I%20have%20tolerated%20this%20and%20not%20done%20anything%20like%20this%2C%20why%20would%20I%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20taken%20Shanno%20into%20custody%20after%20the%20victim's%20family%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20man%20fell%20off%20the%20roof%20during%20a%20fight%20with%20his%20wife.%20His%20body%20has%20been%20kept%20in%20the%20mortuary...We%20have%20taken%20his%20wife%20into%20custody%2C%20and%20the%20investigation%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Akhand%20Pratap%20Singh