doge-global-photos-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla%20Takedown%20demonstrations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20taking%20place%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20better%20question%20for%20Musk%20might%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20built%20my%20showrooms%20in%20a%20way%20that%20made%20them%20such%20ideal%20targets%20for%20demonstrations%3F%26quot%3B%20Because%20the%20answer%20is%3A%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECar%20dealerships%20tend%20to%20be%20relegated%20to%20the%20outskirts%20of%20big%20cities%2C%20but%20most%20of%20Tesla's%20276%20showrooms%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20located%20smack%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20bustling%20neighborhoods%20full%20of%20wealthy%20progressives.%20That%20puts%20them%20right%20next%20to%20popular%20stores%20and%20busy%20restaurants%2C%20increasing%20the%20brand's%20visibility%20and%20foot%20traffic.%20It's%20ideal%20if%20you%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-sales-elon-musk-rebranding-saved-learning-from-airline-disasters-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esell%20a%20status-symbol%20electric%20car%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20maybe%20not%20so%20ideal%20when%20people%20are%20up%20in%20arms%20about%20your%20full-tilt%2C%20questionably%20legal%20operation%20to%20gut%20federal%20services%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20millions%20of%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20put%20his%20showrooms%20in%20tony%20blue%20neighborhoods%20for%20two%20good%20reasons.%20First%2C%20he%20needed%20a%20way%20to%20get%20around%20state%20laws%20that%20bar%20carmakers%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-electric-vehicle-sales-model-automakers-say-wont-catch-on-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eselling%20directly%20to%20consumers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20Musk%20turned%20Tesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cato.org%2Fregulation%2Fsummer-2014%2Ftesla-car-dealers-lobby%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elack%20of%20in-person%20sales%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20selling%20point.%20The%20cars%20at%20a%20Tesla%20%26quot%3Bgallery%26quot%3B%20aren't%20there%20for%20you%20to%20%3Cem%3Ebuy%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Oh%20my%2C%20no!%20The%20grubby%20exchange%20of%20money%20happens%20online.%20That%20means%20that%20unlike%20other%20car%20dealerships%2C%20Musk%20doesn't%20need%20to%20park%20a%20fleet%20of%20unsold%20Hyundais%20along%20some%20six-lane%20highway%20on%20the%20far%20fringes%20of%20town.%20%26quot%3BOur%20stores%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20121024215148%2Fhttp%3A%2Fwww.teslamotors.com%2Fblog%2Ftesla-approach-distributing-and-servicing-cars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMusk%20boasted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202012%2C%20%26quot%3Bare%20designed%20to%20be%20informative%20and%20interactive%20in%20a%20delightful%20way%20and%20are%20simply%20unlike%20the%20traditional%20dealership%20with%20several%20hundred%20cars%20in%20inventory%20that%20a%20commissioned%20salesperson%20is%20tasked%20with%20selling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20Teslas%20are%20designed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-owner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaffluent%2C%20progressive%2C%20early%20adopters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20the%20F-150%20crowd.%20So%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20locate%20the%20showrooms%20where%20the%20customers%20are.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deliberately%20positioning%20our%20store%20and%20gallery%20locations%20in%20high%20foot%20traffic%2C%20high%20visibility%20retail%20venues%2C%20like%20malls%20and%20shopping%20streets%20that%20people%20regularly%20visit%20in%20a%20relatively%20open-minded%20buying%20mood%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20the%20American%20Communities%20Project%2C%20which%20maintains%20a%20county-by-county%20map%20of%20the%20United%20States%20that%20breaks%20out%20demographic%20characteristics%2C%20to%20sync%20its%20data%20with%20the%20locations%20of%20all%20276%20Tesla%20showrooms.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20more%20than%20half%20are%20in%20what%20the%20ACP%20calls%20%26quot%3Bbig%20cities%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Burban%20suburbs.%26quot%3B%20Likewise%2C%20overlaying%20Tesla%20showroom%20locations%20onto%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-zoning-map-home-prices-down-real-estate-new-houses-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eneighborhood%20data%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(courtesy%20of%20the%20National%20Zoning%20Atlas)%20shows%20that%20they're%20predominantly%20in%20census%20tracts%20designated%20as%20%26quot%3Binner%20suburbs.%26quot%3B%20Those%20tracts%20are%20fewer%20than%20a%20third%20of%20all%20neighborhoods%2C%20but%20they're%20home%20to%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Tesla's%20showrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20Tesla%20put%20itself%20in%20places%20where%20people%20are%20better%20educated%2C%20higher-income%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20likely%20to%20vote%20Democratic.%20Which%20means%20that%20Tesla's%20clever%20showrooms%20have%20made%20the%20company%20vulnerable%20to%20protests%20by%20the%20very%20people%20the%20showrooms%20were%20built%20to%20attract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20when%20they%20basically%20won%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20they're%20finding%20a%20way%20to%20lose%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dan%20Crane%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20who%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20book%20%26quot%3BDirect%20Hit%3A%20How%20Tesla%20Went%20Straight%20to%20Consumers%20and%20Smashed%20the%20Car%20Dealers'%20Monopoly.%26quot%3B%20Sales%20are%20down%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-cybertruck-apocalypse-inequality-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECybertrucks%20are%20being%20set%20on%20fire%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-elon-musk-doge-hitting-sales-dan-ives-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla's%20stock%20price%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20plummeted%20by%20more%20than%2030%25%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20retail%20strategy%20made%20them%20sitting%20ducks%2C%26quot%3B%20Crane%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20protested%20car%20dealerships%20before.%20In%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Farchives%2Fla-xpm-2003-aug-23-me-hummers23-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eecological%20activists%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20actually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-and-fall-of-hummer-recession-general-motors-bankruptcy-arnold-schwarzenegger-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eblew%20up%20Hummers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20dealerships%20on%20the%20West%20Coast.%20But%20Tesla%20showrooms%20are%20qualitatively%20different%20from%20those%20of%20its%20rivals.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20actually%20in%20places%20where%20people%20congregate%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dana%20Fisher%2C%20a%20sociologist%20at%20American%20University%20who%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Resistance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20important%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fhistory%2Fgeography-protest-how-urban-design-can-make-or-break-people-power-180975189%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprotest%20strategy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20it%20means%20Tesla%20showrooms%20are%20located%20near%20public%20spaces%20like%20sidewalks%2C%20where%20it's%20legal%20to%20stage%20a%20demonstration.%20Nobody%20has%20to%20trespass%20on%20a%20car%20lot.%20And%20a%20Tesla%20store%20in%20an%20outdoor%20mall%20or%20a%20bustling%20shopping%20street%20puts%20protesters%20right%20in%20the%20faces%20of%20potential%20Tesla%20buyers.%20%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20here%20is%20shaming%20consumers%20about%20their%20purchasing%20decisions%2C%