Stan%20was%20accused%20of%20cutting%20him%20off%20from%20the%20world%20and%20draining%20his%20money.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20creative%2C%20you%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20assured%20his%20daughter.%20%26quot%3BJust%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20weeps%20from%20the%20memory%2C%20as%20she%20often%20does%20when%20she%20talks%20about%20her%20parents.%20The%20voice%20from%20beyond%20captured%20a%20familiar%20dynamic%20between%20her%20and%20Stan%3A%20the%20prolific%2C%20world-conquering%20father%20%E2%80%94%20the%20man%20who%20created%20a%20comic%20book%20%26quot%3Buniverse%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20all%20but%20subsumed%20the%20movie%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20urging%20his%20child%20to%20make%20something%20of%20her%20own%2C%20to%20see%20something%20through.%20It%20was%20advice%2C%20throughout%20her%20life%2C%20that%20she%20had%20experienced%20as%20both%20a%20birthright%20and%20a%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222325%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stan%20Lee%2C%20his%20wife%20Joan%20Lee%2C%20and%20daughter%20Joan%20Celia%20Lee%20pose%20with%20their%20dogs%20ca.%201986%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f58182a466d2b74ab296a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJC%20has%20been%20portrayed%20as%20a%20villain%20who%20exploited%20her%20parents.%20Now%2C%20like%20her%20father%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20life%2C%20she's%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20from%20Stan%20Lee's%20empire.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knows%20I'm%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20JC%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20recounts%20the%20seance%20to%20me%20not%20long%20after%20we%20first%20meet%2C%20at%20her%20home%20in%20the%20Hollywood%20Hills.%20She%20had%20invited%20me%20to%20visit%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20share%20her%20story%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Since%20her%20father%20died%20at%20age%2095%2C%20JC%20has%20been%20widely%20portrayed%20as%20a%20villain%20in%20the%20Stan%20Lee%20story%3A%20the%20spoiled%2C%20impossible%20child%20who%20exploited%20her%20father%2C%20and%20then%20failed%20to%20protect%20him%20in%20his%20final%20years.%20In%20the%20months%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Stan%20said%20he%20was%20surrounded%20by%20%26quot%3Bunscrupulous%20businessmen%2C%20sycophants%2C%20and%20opportunists%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20JC%20had%20done%20nothing%20to%20stop%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20like%20her%20dad%20in%20his%20later%20years%2C%20JC%20is%20alone.%20Her%20family%20is%20mostly%20gone%2C%20and%20she's%20fallen%20out%20with%20her%20many%20famous%20friends.%20Her%20circle%20has%20grown%20small%2C%20and%20the%20people%20who%20surround%20her%20and%20keep%20her%20company%20have%20business%20ties%20to%20her%20or%20her%20father.%20I%20wonder%20if%20JC's%20story%20is%20one%20of%20history%20repeating%20itself.%20Others%2C%20I%20learn%2C%20have%20similar%20worries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20thing%20JC%20inherited%20from%20her%20father%20is%20she%20has%20a%20real%20knack%20for%20surrounding%20herself%20with%20con%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jonathan%20Bolerjack%2C%20one%20of%20Stan's%20closest%20confidants%20in%20his%20final%20months%20who's%20known%20JC%20for%20years.%20%26quot%3BThey%20both%20have%20this%20uncanny%20ability%20to%20be%20very%20trusting%20and%20yet%20find%20themselves%20surrounded%20by%20the%20worst%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20being%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20world%2C%20after%20having%20existed%20for%20so%20many%20years%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%2C%20and%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%2C%20powerful%20men%3A%20not%20only%20her%20father%2C%20but%20a%20string%20of%20boyfriends%2C%20business%20associates%2C%20advisors.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knows%20I'm%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20talk.%20I'm%20ruled%20by%20the%20men.%20That's%20the%20bottom%20line.%26quot%3B%20She%20can't%20understand%20how%20she%20got%20here%20%E2%80%94%20how%20her%20father's%20wealth%20and%20fame%20and%20creative%20energy%20have%20eluded%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20it%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20none%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EJC's%20gated%20property%20sits%20on%20half%20an%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20surrounded%20by%20towering%20palm%20trees.%20Inside%2C%20though%2C%20the%20house%20feels%20strangely%20devoid%20of%20life.%20What%20passes%20for%20interior%20design%20is%20mostly%20Marvel%20kitsch.%20The%20marble-floored%20entryway%20boasts%20not%20one%20but%20three%20lifesize%20models%20of%20Spider-Man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPages%20of%20her%20own%20artwork%20are%20scattered%20everywhere.%20They're%20lovely%20%E2%80%94%20abstract%2C%20wavy%20designs%20sketched%20in%20colored%20pencil%20and%20crayon.%20She's%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20her%20drawings%20and%20paintings%20up%20for%20sale%2C%20treating%20them%20more%20as%20items%20to%20be%20stored%20than%20creations%20to%20be%20displayed.%20In%20the%20garage%2C%20there%20are%20stacks%20upon%20stacks%20of%20paintings%20she%20has%20done%20over%20the%20decades.%20Even%20more%2C%20she%20tells%20me%2C%20are%20gathering%20dust%20in%20her%20parents'%20home%20up%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20Spidermen%20at%20Stan%20Lee's%20House%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f6e1a5a466d2b74ab2bd05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJC's%20home%20in%20the%20exclusive%20Bird%20Streets%20neighborhood%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20Hills%20has%20an%20unfinished%2C%20barely%20lived-in%20quality%20to%20it.%3Cp%3EAdam%20Latham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20shows%20me%20around%20the%20house%2C%20her%20two%20dogs%2C%20Duchess%20and%20Rodent%2C%20follow%20at%20our%20heels.%20There's%20a%20screening%20room%2C%20a%20pool%2C%20and%20a%20sauna.%20When%20she%20ushers%20me%20into%20what%20she%20calls%20the%20master%20bedroom%2C%20I%20wonder%20if%20I%20misheard%3A%20The%20room%20has%20no%20furniture%20to%20speak%20of%2C%20not%20even%20a%20bed.%20The%20master%20bathroom%20has%20no%20sink.%20Seeing%20my%20puzzlement%2C%20JC%20explains%20that%20there%20was%20a%20leak%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20that%20nearly%20ruined%20the%20place%2C%20and%20ever%20since%20she's%20been%20sleeping%20in%20a%20guest%20room%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20house.%20She%20doesn't%20know%20why%20there%20aren't%20any%20sinks%20in%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20many%20projects%20that%20consume%20her%20remain%20stuck%20in%20the%20concept%20phase.%20Most%20of%20them%2C%20which%20speak%20to%20JC's%20immediate%20preoccupations%2C%20don't%20seem%20to%20hold%20much%20commercial%20appeal.%20She%20has%20an%20idea%20for%20a%20board%20game%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20where%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20holds%20the%20copyright%20to%20her%20father's%20name.%20She%20calls%20it%20%26quot%3BWhere%20Is%20Stan%20Lee%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20Broadway%20musical%20she%20wants%20to%20create%20about%20Stan's%20life%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20focuses%20not%20on%20the%20golden%20age%20of%20Marvel%2C%20but%20on%20the%20sad%2C%20final%20years%20before%20his%20death.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20Shakespearean%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20preoccupation%20is%20money.%20JC%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20know%20how%20much%20of%20it%20she%20has%2C%20or%20how%20long%20it%20will%20last.%20She%20charges%20everything%20to%20an%20Amex%20card.%20I%20can't%20tell%20if%20she%20has%20willingly%20outsourced%20the%20details%20of%20her%20finances%20to%20others%2C%20or%20if%20whoever%20is%20holding%20the%20purse%20strings%20is%20deliberately%20keeping%20her%20out%20of%20the%20loop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20talk%2C%20two%20friends%20of%20JC's%20keep%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20us.%20Jesse%20Gargiulo%2C%20her%20close%20companion%20and%20hairdresser%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20serves%20as%20something%20of%20an%20unofficial%20spokesman.%20He%20looks%20like%20a%201970s%20TV%20star%2C%20with%20thick%20black%20hair%2C%20a%20deep%20California%20tan%2C%20and%20an%20easygoing%20demeanor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20is%20Eymun%20Talasazan%2C%20who%20is%20visibly%20annoyed%20at%20my%20presence.%20Tall%20and%20well-built%2C%20he's%20clearly%20the%20alpha%20of%20the%20three.%20When%20I%20arrived%2C%20he%20seemed%20reluctant%20to%20shake%20my%20hand%3B%20I%20find%20out%20later%20he%20had%20no%20idea%20I%20was%20coming.%20Talasazan's%20father%20owned%20an%20antique%20business%20that%20JC's%20mother%20liked%20to%20patronize%2C%20and%20Talasazan%2C%20who%20dabbles%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20was%20the%20listing%20agent%20for%20one%20of%20Stan's%20properties%20in%202015.%20He%20tells%20me%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20the%20story%2C%20but%20he%20makes%20a%20point%20of%20leaning%20in%20close%20and%20instructing%20me%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20JC%20comes%20out%20looking%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20JC%20tells%20me%20she%20isn't%20feeling%20well%20and%20suggests%20I%20come%20back%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20Gargiulo%20sees%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20another%20day%20in%20paradise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22J.C.%20Lee%204%20years%20old%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f5834dc6ad288d147d94a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221394%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20as%20a%20child%2C%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Joan%26quot%3B%20longed%20to%20make%20her%20father%20proud.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20been%20terribly%20ambitious%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Stan%20Lee%20Papers%2C%20American%20Heritage%20Center%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wyoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20as%20long%20as%20Joan%20Celia%20Lee%20can%20remember%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20like%20her%20dad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20JC%20was%20born%20in%201950%2C%20Stan%20already%20had%20a%20successful%20career%20writing%20for%20Timely%20Comics%2C%20which%20later%20would%20be%20renamed%20Marvel.%20Her%20mother%2C%20Joan%20Boocock%2C%20was%20a%20British%20hat%20model%20and%20actor.%20JC%20was%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Joan%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20mother's%20%26quot%3BBig%20Joan%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20distinction%20that%20grew%20funnier%20as%20JC%20became%20the%20taller%20of%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20JC%20was%203%2C%20her%20newborn%20sister%20died.%20Stan%20and%20Joan%20channeled%20their%20grief%20into%20becoming%20overprotective%20parents%20to%20JC.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20cross-eyed.%20I%20wore%20glasses.%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20misfit.%20I%20was%20too%20skinny%2C%26quot%3B%20JC%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BFor%20a%20while%2C%20my%20father%20would%20bring%20home%20a%20milkshake%20every%20day%20to%20get%20me%20to%20gain%20weight.%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20animals.%26quot%3B%20When%20a%20chimpanzee%20on%20roller%20skates%20appeared%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ed%20Sullivan%20Show%2C%26quot%3B%20Stan%20cried%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20get%20that%20chimp!%26quot%3B%20But%20when%20the%20family%20went%20to%20fetch%20their%20new%20pet%2C%20it%20immediately%20made%20a%20pass%20at%20Big%20Joan.%20%26quot%3BIt%20grabbed%20her%20bosom%2C%26quot%3B%20JC%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20horny.%26quot%3B%20Stan%20had%20a%20change%20of%20heart.%20%26quot%3BNo%20monkey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20announced.%20Instead%2C%20JC%20wound%20up%20getting%20a%20parrot%20that%20spoke%20Spanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201961%2C%20with%20the%20release%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fantastic%20Four%2C%26quot%3B%20Stan%20became%20a%20full-fledged%20celebrity.%20The%20elder%20child%20of%20Jewish%20immigrants%2C%20he%20had%20imagined%20his%20way%20to%20fame%2C%20creating%20a%20world%20of%20superheroes%20that%20became%20a%20signature%20of%20American%20culture.%20From%20an%20early%20age%2C%20JC%20yearned%20to%20follow%20in%20his%20footsteps.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20been%20terribly%20ambitious%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20Marvel%20and%20in%20Stan's%20world%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20a%20writer%20and%20I%20wasn't%20an%20artist%2C%20so%20what%20was%20I%20going%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20she%20might%20pursue%20a%20career%20onstage%2C%20she%20enrolled%20at%20the%20Professional%20Children's%20School%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20which%20catered%20to%20child%20actors%20and%20dancers.%20One%20of%20her%20classmates%2C%20Lorna%20Luft%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Judy%20Garland%2C%20remembers%20JC%20as%20a%20free%20spirit.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20so%20stunning%2C%20and%20so%20pretty%2C%20and%20so%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuft%20recalls%20visiting%20the%20Lees%20at%20their%20cottage%20in%20Hewlett%20Harbor%20and%20seeing%20Stan%20at%20work%20at%20an%20easel%20by%20the%20pool.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20the%20pool%20filter%20made%20this%20bubbling%20noise%2C%20and%20he%20went%2C%20'Oh%2C%20Jesus!'%20I%20asked%2C%20'Are%20you%20OK%2C%20Mr.%20Lee%3F'%20And%20he%20said%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20but%20in%20my%20mind%20it%20was%20a%20sea%20monster!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%2C%20OK%2C%20he's%20a%20little%20strange%2C%26quot%3B%20Luft%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20know%20what%20he%20did%20for%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Stan's%20success%20grew%2C%20the%20pampering%20of%20JC%20became%20more%20lavish.%20%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20is%20not%20sensible%20and%20cautious%2C%20and%20I%20am%20not%20sensible%20and%20cautious%2C%26quot%3B%20Joan%20would%20say.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20spend%20his%20money%20gleefully.%26quot%3B%20JC%20describes%20her%20attitude%20toward%20personal%20finance%20in%20similar%20terms.%20%26quot%3BMy%20lifestyle%20is%20extravagant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20my%20father%20was%20Stan%20Lee%20and%20his%20wife%20was%20a%20great%20diva%20and%20elegant%20and%20first%20class%20all%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20shared%20a%20name%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20JC's%20personality%20was%20closer%20to%20Stan's.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20both%20overwhelming%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Larry%20Leiber%2C%20Stan's%2093-year-old%20brother%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BThey%20both%20have%20a%20strong%20presence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221827%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22J.C.%20Lee%20on%20the%20cover%20of%20Intimate%20Romances%20Magazine%20from%201975%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f58586c6ad288d147d954f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJC%20dabbled%20in%20modeling%20and%20acting%2C%20but%20never%20managed%20to%20break%20through.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Stan%20Lee%20Papers%2C%20American%20Heritage%20Center%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wyoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20grew%20older%2C%20JC%20had%20trouble%20finding%20her%20way.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20debutante%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20had%20two%20passionate%20parents.%26quot%3B%20She%20enrolled%20at%20the%20American%20Academy%20of%20Dramatic%20Arts%2C%20but%20dropped%20out%20after%20a%20year.%20She%20did%20some%20modeling%2C%20and%20her%20parents%20set%20her%20up%20in%20an%20apartment%20across%20the%20hall%20from%20theirs.%20At%20one%20point%20Stan%20got%20her%20a%20job%20at%20Marvel%20as%20a%20receptionist.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20say%20to%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Roy%20Thomas%2C%20a%20writer%20at%20Marvel%20who%20later%20succeeded%20Stan%20as%20editor.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20the%20boss'%20daughter%2C%20so%20you're%20kind%20of%20wary%20you'll%20say%20the%20wrong%20thing.%26quot%3B%20His%20impression%20was%20that%20%26quot