n%201998%2C%20as%20Stan%20prepared%20to%20exit%20day-to-day%20operations%20at%20Marvel%2C%20he%20signed%20a%20contract%20that%20set%20him%20up%20with%20an%20annual%20salary%20that%20would%20cap%20at%20%241%20million%20a%20year%20for%20life%2C%20stock%20options%2C%20and%2010%25%20of%20the%20profits%20from%20any%20movies%20that%20used%20Marvel%20characters%20he%20had%20helped%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20last%20clause%2C%20had%20he%20held%20on%20to%20it%2C%20would%20have%20been%20a%20gold%20mine.%20In%202002%2C%20%26quot%3BSpider-Man%2C%26quot%3B%20starring%20Tobey%20Maguire%2C%20became%20a%20box%20office%20sensation%2C%20grossing%20over%20%24825%20million%20worldwide.%20But%20when%20Stan%20didn't%20receive%20his%20promised%2010%25%2C%20he%20sued.%20In%20a%20settlement%20signed%20in%202005%2C%20Stan%20agreed%20to%20drop%20the%20profit-share%20agreement%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20one-time%20lump%20sum%20of%20%2410%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Stan%2C%20who%20was%20in%20his%2080s%2C%20it%20must%20have%20seemed%20like%20a%20generous%20deal.%20Instead%2C%20he%20had%20given%20away%20the%20keys%20to%20his%20kingdom.%20The%20Marvel%20Cinematic%20Universe%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20highest-grossing%20film%20franchise.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20Stan's%20death%2C%20his%20comic%20book%20creations%20had%20raked%20in%20close%20to%20%2430%20billion%20at%20the%20box%20office%20%E2%80%94%20including%20six%20of%20the%2020%20highest-grossing%20movies%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Stan%20didn't%20own%20the%20iconic%20Marvel%20characters%20he%20helped%20create%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20keep%20working%20into%20his%2090s%20to%20maintain%20his%20lifestyle.%20Most%20of%20his%20money%20came%20from%20trying%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20his%20name.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20formed%20Stan%20Lee%20Media%2C%20followed%20by%20POW%20Entertainment.%20Both%20quickly%20descended%20into%20scandal%2C%20accused%20of%20mismanagement%20and%20ripping%20off%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20tried%20launching%20a%20few%20ventures%20of%20her%20own%2C%20including%20a%20jewelry%20line%20and%20a%20brief%20foray%20as%20a%20recording%20artist.%20But%20her%20most%20successful%20projects%20were%20those%20that%20relied%20on%20her%20father's%20name.%20She%20published%20a%20photo%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BStan%20Lee's%20Love%20Story%3A%20It's%20All%20About%20Love%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20launched%20a%20company%20selling%20%26quot%3BI%20Love%20Stan%26quot%3B%20T-shirts%20at%20comic%20conventions%20for%20%2420%20a%20pop.%20But%20according%20to%20James%20MacLean%2C%20her%20partner%20in%20the%20enterprise%2C%20JC%20lost%20interest%20in%20the%20business%20when%20she%20learned%20they%20would%20have%20to%20recoup%20their%20initial%20investment%20before%20she%20would%20see%20any%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20happened%20she%20stopped%20supporting%20the%20T-shirt%2C%26quot%3B%20MacLean%20says.%20%26quot%3BAny%20time%20her%20dad%20did%20something%2C%20there%20was%20always%20a%20lot%20of%20cash%20around%2C%20so%20that%20was%20her%20expectation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EA%20devastating%20blow%20arrived%20in%202017%2C%20when%20Big%20Joan%20suffered%20a%20stroke%20and%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2095.%20JC%20had%20lost%20her%20best%20friend%20at%20the%20very%20moment%20her%20father's%20wealth%20was%20drying%20up.%20Arguments%20over%20money%20between%20JC%20and%20Stan%20were%20starting%20to%20escalate%20into%20full-scale%20shouting%20matches%2C%20and%20Big%20Joan%20had%20been%20the%20only%20one%20who%20could%20defuse%20the%20tension.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20and%20sad%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20MacLean%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEight%20months%20later%2C%20stories%20began%20appearing%20in%20the%20press%20that%20painted%20a%20dire%20picture%20of%20Stan's%20life%2C%20including%20accusations%20that%20his%20closest%20confidants%20were%20fleecing%20him.%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%20presented%20a%20particularly%20unflattering%20portrait%20of%20JC%2C%20describing%20hysterical%20demands%20for%20money%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowder-keg%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20her%20father.%20The%20story%20included%20an%20allegation%20by%20Bradley%20Herman%2C%20Stan's%20former%20business%20manager%2C%20who%20accused%20JC%20of%20attacking%20her%20parents%20in%202014%2C%20after%20she%20discovered%20that%20her%20new%20Jaguar%20was%20actually%20leased%20in%20her%20father's%20name.%20As%20the%20argument%20escalated%2C%20Herman%20alleged%2C%20JC%20had%20violently%20grabbed%20Big%20Joan's%20arm%20and%20slammed%20Stan's%20head%20against%20the%20back%20of%20a%20chair.%20Herman%20provided%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%20with%20photos%20of%20a%20bruise%20on%20Big%20Joan's%20arm%2C%20but%20said%20the%20Lees%20had%20told%20him%20not%20to%20go%20to%20the%20authorities%20because%20their%20daughter%20was%20in%20a%20fragile%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22JC%20Lee%20and%20Stan%20Lee%20appear%20on%20stage%20together%20at%20Silicon%20Valley%20Comic%20Con.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f7ee3fa466d2b74ab2cfc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJC%20and%20Stan%20at%20an%20event%20in%202016.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20press%20reports%20would%20say%20she%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowder-keg%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20her%20father.%3Cp%3EKelly%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJC%2C%20who%20can%20be%20volatile%20and%20prone%20to%20fly%20off%20the%20handle%2C%20concedes%20that%20she%20often%20screamed%20at%20her%20parents%2C%20usually%20over%20money%2C%20but%20she%20vehemently%20denies%20hitting%20them.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20ever%20touched%20my%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lie.%26quot%3B%20Five%20people%20I%20spoke%20with%20who%20were%20close%20to%20Stan%20at%20the%20time%20told%20me%20they%20never%20saw%20JC%20commit%20any%20physical%20abuse.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20equally%20abusive%2C%20the%20way%20they%20screamed%20at%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20MacLean%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20it%20would%20be%20like%2C%20'Let's%20sit%20down%20and%20have%20dinner.'%20That%20was%20their%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Big%20Joan%20gone%2C%20Stan%20grew%20increasingly%20isolated.%20By%202018%2C%20the%20people%20in%20his%20inner%20circle%20had%20been%20driven%20out.%20That%20August%2C%20a%20few%20months%20before%20Stan's%20death%2C%20he%20obtained%20a%20restraining%20order%20against%20his%20new%20business%20manager%2C%20Keya%20Morgan%2C%20who%20was%20later%20charged%20with%20stealing%20from%20his%20client.%20(The%20case%20was%20dismissed%20after%20a%20jury%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20verdict.)%20One%20of%20the%20world's%20greatest%20artists%20was%20abandoned%20and%20alone%2C%20with%20only%20his%20daughter%20by%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20Bolerjack%2C%20a%20long-haired%20comic%20book%20fan%20who%20had%20been%20part%20of%20Stan's%20entourage%20on%20the%20convention%20circuit%20for%20years%2C%20got%20a%20call%20from%20JC.%20In%20the%20background%2C%20he%20could%20hear%20Stan%20calling%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20that%20Hairspray%3F%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20nickname%20Stan%20had%20given%20him.%20Bolerjack%2C%20who%20hadn't%20seen%20his%20friend%20in%20months%2C%20rushed%20over%20to%20the%20house.%20The%20comic%20book%20icon%20looked%20to%20have%20aged%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20sat%20me%20down%20and%20said%3A%20'I've%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20bad%20decisions%20with%20people%20lately%20and%20I%20keep%20getting%20betrayed.%20I%20just%20need%20you%20to%20help%20me%2C'%26quot%3B%20Bolerjack%20tells%20me%2C%20choking%20up%20at%20the%20recollection.%20%26quot%3BHe%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20he%20said%2C%20'Please%20don't%20let%20me%20down.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20six%20months%20of%20Stan's%20life%2C%20Bolerjack%20showed%20up%20nearly%20every%20afternoon%2C%20and%20earlier%20on%20weekends%2C%20to%20stay%20with%20Stan%20until%20late%20in%20the%20evening.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20just%20an%20old%20man%2C%20a%20guy%20that%20you%20love%2C%20who%20is%20just%20so%20battered%20by%20things%20and%20asks%20you%20to%20please%20don't%20let%20him%20down%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20such%20an%20emotionally%20weighted%20request%20that%20I%20took%20it%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bolerjack.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20Stan%20would%20sit%20on%20his%20couch%20and%20look%20out%20at%20his%20pool%2C%20seemingly%20haunted%20by%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20remembers%20her%20father's%20final%20days%20as%20filled%20with%20regret.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20time%20he%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20couch%2C%20he%20never%20had%20any%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20worried%20about%20me.%20Were%20there%20any%20happy%20moments%20at%20the%20end%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%20I%20wish%20there%20was.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2012%2C%202018%2C%20Stan%20Lee%20collapsed%20at%20his%20home.%20JC%2C%20arriving%20for%20a%20visit%20with%20her%20father%2C%20pulled%20into%20his%20driveway%20just%20as%20he%20was%20being%20loaded%20into%20an%20ambulance%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital.%20%26quot%3BThey%20wanted%20to%20do%20all%20these%20terrible%20things%20to%20his%20body%20to%20see%20if%20they%20could%20bring%20him%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%20no.%20He%20appeared%20to%20be%20gone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStan%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20from%20a%20heart%20attack.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20her%20life%2C%20Little%20Joan%2C%20the%20sole%20heir%20to%20what%20remained%20of%20Stan's%20empire%2C%20was%20truly%20on%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20second%20visit%20to%20JC's%20house%2C%20I%20stop%20by%20Stan%20and%20Joan's%20home%20in%20the%20exclusive%20Bird%20Streets%20neighborhood%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20Hills.%20Imagining%20the%20Xanadu%20of%20a%20comic%20titan%20%E2%80%94%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20is%20a%20neighbor%20%E2%80%94%20I%20instead%20find%20the%20place%20in%20a%20state%20of%20disrepair.%20The%20house%20is%20missing%20siding%2C%20and%20Big%20Joan's%20once%20meticulous%20landscaping%20is%20overgrown.%20Incongruously%2C%20two%20pristine%20cars%20sit%20in%20the%20driveway.%20I%20wonder%20who%20is%20using%20Stan's%20oasis%20as%20a%20parking%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222419%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Facade%20of%20Stan%20and%20Joan%20home%20in%20the%20Hollywood%20Hills%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f587d5c6ad288d147d95ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20pair%20of%20cars%20parked%20outside%20Stan%20and%20Joan's%20home%20belong%20to%20an%20associate%20of%20JC's%20advisor%2C%20Eymun%20Talasazan.%3Cp%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20get%20to%20JC's%20house%2C%20I%20find%20her%20in%20the%20same%20spot%20as%20before%2C%20sitting%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20couch%20and%20sipping%20a%20Heineken.%20I%20notice%20that%20a%20chair%20with%20worn%20green%20fabric%20has%20been%20brought%20into%20the%20room.%20JC%20tells%20me%20it%20was%20a%20favorite%20of%20Stan's%2C%20and%20invites%20me%20to%20sit%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20her%20father's%20death%2C%20JC%20tells%20me%2C%20she's%20been%20frozen%20out%20by%20those%20who%20control%20her%20father's%20legacy.%20Her%20stake%20in%20the%20Stan%20Lee%20Universe%2C%20now%20controlled%20by%20a%20company%20called%20Kartoon%20Studios%2C%20is%20less%20than%205%25.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20JC%20reached%20out%20to%20Kartoon%20about%20being%20more%20involved%20in%20the%20business%2C%20but%20those%20conversations%20ultimately%20disintegrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20is%20supporting%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20JC%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20these%20people%20have%20taken%20my%20life%2C%20and%20they're%20eating%20off%20gold%20utensils%20and%20I'm%20eating%20off%20plastic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Heyward%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Kartoon%2C%20had%20a%20relationship%20with%20Stan%20that%20dated%20back%20to%20the%201980s.%20He%20recalls%20Stan's%20%26quot%3Bconstant%26quot%3B%20complaints%20about%20JC's%20spending%20and%20considers%20her%20spoiled.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20in%20any%20more%20state%20of%20business%20with%20her%20than%20we%20currently%20are%2C%20where%20she%20is%20a%20passive%20participant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20we%20can't%20just%20go%20on%20through%20life%20saying%20we're%20a%20victim%20of%20whatever%20made%20us%20the%20way%20we%20are.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20you're%20an%20adult%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20who%20you%20choose%20to%20be%20and%20how%20you%20live%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20has%20made%20other%20attempts%20to%20gain%20control%20of%20Stan's%20empire.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20she%20sued%20POW%20in%20federal%20court%2C%20claiming%20her%20father's%20business%20partners%20had%20misled%20him%20about%20deals%20that%20signed%20away%20the%20rights%20to%20his%20name%20and%20likeness.%20In%202020%2C%20a%20judge%20dismissed%20her%20lawsuit%20as%20%26quot%3Bfrivolous%26quot%3B%20and%20ordered%20her%20to%20pay%20%241%20million%20%E2%80%94%20though%20that%20sanction%20was%20later%20tossed%20out%20by%20a%20higher%20court.%20In%202023%2C%20JC%20sued%20POW%20again%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20Lee%20Trust%2C%20which%20she%20controls%2C%20should%20have%20a%20greater%20share%20in%20the%20company.%20The%20case%20is%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuits%20strike%20those%20who%20know%20her%20as%20another%20sign%20of%20her%20lifelong%20desire%20to%20win%20her%20father's%20approval.%20%26quot%3BShe%20just%20really%20wanted%20to%20know%20Stan%20was%20proud%20of%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Bolerjack%20says.%20%26quot%3BShe%20wanted%20to%20make%20her%20dad%20proud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20legal%20setbacks%2C%20JC%20remains%20buzzing%20with%20ideas%2C%20but%20short%20on%20allies.%20As%20I%20sit%20with%20her%2C%20she%20is%20once%20again%20accompanied%20by%20Gargiulo%2C%20her%20longtime%20friend%2C%20and%20Talasazan%2C%20who%20she%20tells%20me%20is%20serving%20as%20an%20informal%20financial%20advisor.%20Talasazan%20seems%20as%20grumpy%20about%20my%20presence%20as%20he%20was%20on%20my%20first%20visit.%20With%20him%20is%20a%20friend%20who%2C%20I%20learn%20later%2C%20was%20the%20one%20who'd%20parked%20the%20vintage%20cars%20in%20Stan's%20driveway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20of%20those%20who%20circled%20around%20Stan%20before%20his%20death%2C%20both%20Gargiulo%20and%20Talasazan%20have%20made%20efforts%20to%20involve%20themselves%20in%20Lee's%20business%20empire.%20Toward%20the%20end%20of%20Stan's%20life%2C%20JC%20set%20up%20a%20meeting%20so%20Gargiulo%20could%20pitch%20her%20father%20on%20a%20superhero%20movie%20he%20hoped%20to%20produce%20with%20JC.%20As%20Gargiulo%20recounts%20it%2C%20Stan%20looked%20at%20him%20and%20put%20his%20hand%20on%20Gargiulo's%20knee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20is%20this%20going%20to%20help%20my%20daughter%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Garguilo%20assured%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOK%2C%20that's%20all%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20He%20gave%20the%20project%20his%20blessing%2C%20but%20nothing%20ever%20came%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalasazan%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20been%20trailed%20by%20controversy.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20made%20headlines%20when%20he%20took%20the%20R%26amp%3BB%20artist%20The%20Weeknd%20to%20court%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20artist's%20Marvel%20comic%20book%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marvel.com%2Farticles%2Fcomics%2Fthe-weeknd-presents-starboy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarboy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20his%20chart-topping%20album%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20had%20been%20Talasazan's%20idea.%20(He%20dropped%20the%20lawsuit%20a%20year%20later).%20In%202021%2C%20a%20court%20issued%20a%20default%20judgment%20against%20Talasazan%20for%20defrauding%20a%20teenager%20and%20ordered%20him%20to%20pay%20%24633%2C380.%20Another%20lawsuit%20against%20him%2C%20which%20is%20still%20pending%2C%20alleges%20that%20he%20failed%20to%20repay%20more%20than%20%24300%2C000%20in%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20including%20legal%20fees%20to%20fight%20the%20previous%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacLean%2C%20JC's%20partner%20in%20the%20T-shirt%20business%2C%20recalls%20Talasazan%20as%20an%20aggressive%20salesman%20while%20Stan%20and%20Joan%20were%20still%20alive.%20%26quot%3BHe%20would%20bring%20stuff%20from%20his%20dad's%2C%20a%20carload%20of%20antiques%2C%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20Mrs.%20Lee%2C%20this%20is%20so%20nice.'%20She%20was%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20pain%20and%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20medication%20and%20she%20would%20buy%20a%20lot%20of%20antiques.%26quot%3B%20There%20were%20so%20many%20pieces%2C%20JC%20tells%20me%2C%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20family%20home%20wound%20up%20looking%20like%20a%20furniture%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGargiulo%20is%20worried%20that%20Talasazan%20is%20taking%20advantage%20of%20JC.%20He%20says%20Talasazan%20has%20been%20gutting%20Stan%20and%20Joan's%20house%20and%20putting%20the%20contents%20in%20a%20loft%20in%20downtown%20Los%20Angeles.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20watch%20somebody%20you%20really%20care%20about%20be%20abused%20by%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Gargiulo%20says.%20%26quot%3BEymun%20just%20screams%20at%20JC%20about%20doing%20what%20has%20to%20be%20done%20and%20'signing%20these%20papers.'%20I%20would%20say%2C%20'There's%20no%20reason%20to%20scream%20at%20her.'%20There's%20something%20not%20right%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20acknowledges%20that%20Talasazan%20sometimes%20screams%20at%20her%2C%20but%20she%20brushes%20it%20off%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Bpassionate%20Persian%20way.%26quot%3B%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20interrupts%20a%20voicemail%20message%20she's%20leaving%20me%20to%20take%20a%20call%20from%20Talasazan%20on%20another%20phone%2C%20and%20I%20can%20overhear%20him%20swearing%20at%20her.%20%26quot%3BJust%20shut%20your%20mouth!%26quot%3B%20he%20yells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJC%20tells%20me%20that%20Talasazan%20convinced%20her%20to%20list%20her%20home%20for%20sale%20last%20year%20for%20%248.8%20million.%20%26quot%3BI%20need%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20He's%20also%20helping%20her%20assemble%20a%20new%20team%20of%20lawyers%20and%20business%20partners%20to%20reclaim%20her%20father's%20empire.%20She's%20never%20met%20them%2C%20but%20Talasazan%20has%20assured%20her%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bbona%20fide%20billionaires%26quot%3B%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20help%20me%20with%20retrieving%20my%20money.%26quot%3B%20She's%20unclear%20on%20precisely%20how%20they%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Talasazan%20%E2%80%94%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%20supporting%20her%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22LOS%20ANGELES%20-%20JUNE%2022%3A%20Creator%20Stan%20Lee's%20daughter%20attend%20the%20premiere%20of%20the%20Sony%20film%20%26quot%3BSpider-Man%202%26quot%3B%20on%20June%2022%2C%202004%20at%20the%20Mann%20Village%20Theater%2C%20in%20Westwood%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f588d1c6ad288d147d962d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221225%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMuch%20like%20Stan%20in%20his%20later%20years%2C%20JC%20has%20left%20her%20finances%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20others.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20men%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20a%20lot%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EVince%20Bucci%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEymun%2C%20when%20I%20call%20him%2C%20he's%20at%20the%20computer%20and%20he's%20working%20endlessly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20men%20things.%20I%20don't%20understand%20a%20lot%20of%20this.%20He%20does.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGargiulo%20tells%20me%20that%20my%20visit%20contributed%20to%20a%20rift%20between%20him%20and%20Talasazan%2C%20who%20warned%20him%20to%20stop%20bringing%20people%20to%20the%20house.%20Otherwise%2C%20Talasazan%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20out%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20a%20part%20of%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Gargiulo%20says%20he%20responded.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20my%20friend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalasazan%20arranged%20a%20time%20to%20speak%20with%20me%2C%20but%20then%20stopped%20responding%20to%20my%20calls%20and%20texts.%20When%20I%20tell%20JC%20that%20her%20current%20situation%20feels%20eerily%20similar%20to%20what%20her%20father%20went%20through%2C%20she%20ponders%20for%20a%20moment.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20dead%20in%20the%20water%20if%20not%20for%20E%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20of%20Talasazan.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20find%20imperfect%2C%20you%20can%20always%20find%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%2C%20like%20many%20heiresses%2C%20JC%20really%20never%20had%20a%20shot%20at%20a%20normal%20life.%20When%20you're%20born%20into%20a%20famous%20family%2C%20as%20Lorna%20Luft%20tells%20me%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20inherit%20the%20fame.%26quot%3B%20JC%20also%20appears%20to%20have%20inherited%20the%20worst%20aspects%20of%20both%20her%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20her%20mother's%20penchant%20for%20spending%20money%2C%20and%20her%20father's%20poor%20judgment%20about%20making%20it.%20As%20her%20father%20was%20during%20his%20latter%20years%2C%20she%20is%20largely%20alone%2C%20cut%20off%20from%20friends%20and%20family.%20She%20speaks%20on%20the%20phone%20from%20time%20to%20time%20with%20her%20uncle%2C%20Stan's%20brother%20Larry%2C%20who%20still%20lives%20in%20Manhattan.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20sad%20that%20we%20weren't%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20Larry%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20we're%20able%20to%20talk%20now%20because%20she%20wants%20family.%20At%20my%20age%2C%20I%20can't%20come%20to%20California%20and%20slay%20dragons.%20But%20I%20do%20care%20about%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20Stan's%20brother%20brought%20me%20back%20to%20my%20final%20visit%20with%20JC.%20As%20I%20sat%20across%20from%20her%20in%20Stan's%20favorite%20chair%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20how%20many%20times%20he%20must%20have%20sat%20on%20the%20same%20worn%20green%20fabric%2C%20looking%20across%20at%20his%20daughter%2C%20worried%20about%20what%20would%20become%20of%20her%2C%20his%20little%20girl%20who%20had%20never%20truly%20managed%20to%20find%20her%20way%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20tried%20to%20give%20her%20everything%2C%20and%20he%20left%20her%20with%20next%20to%20nothing.%20For%20JC%2C%20the%20privilege%20he%20provided%20her%20is%20inseparable%20from%20the%20pain%20she%20has%20suffered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20wonderful%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20knew%20I'd%20pay%20a%20price%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjason-guerrasio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJason%20Guerrasio%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20an%20entertainment%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-life-marvel-legend-stan-lee-daughter-spiderman-xmen-business-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744532221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f5839c3fe8d39283627de8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-life-marvel-legend-stan-lee-daughter-spiderman-xmen-business-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stan%2