20founding%2C%20the%20company%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECurtis%20Priem%20has%20always%20been%20forward-looking%20man.%20Even%20in%20the%20nascent%20days%20of%20computer%20graphics%20and%20video%20games%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20great%20potential%20that%20lay%20ahead%20for%20visual%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriem%20poured%20his%20time%20and%20energy%20into%20graphics%20technology%2C%20creating%20the%20first%20graphics%20processor%20for%20a%20PC%2C%20the%20IBM%20Professional%20Graphics%20Adapter%2C%20according%20to%20his%20alma%20mater%2C%20Rensselaer%20Polytechnic%20Institute%20(RPI).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20one%20event%20upon%20which%20Priem%20looks%20back%20with%20regret%3A%20had%20he%20held%20onto%20all%20of%20the%20stock%20he%20once%20owned%20in%20the%20AI%2C%20software%2C%20and%20computer%20hardware%20juggernaut%20Nvidia%2C%20he%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20people%20alive%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20north%20of%20%2470%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fphoebeliu%2F2023%2F11%2F26%2Fthis-nvidia-cofounder-could-have-been-worth-70-billion-instead-he-lives-off-the-grid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Priem%20is%20now%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%2430%20million%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%20enough%20to%20keep%20him%20living%20in%20comfort.%20Priem%20lives%20in%20an%20off-the-grid%20house%20near%20Fremont%2C%20California%2C%20not%20far%20from%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20company%20he%20co-founded%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224125c20f-eab3-49cc-8987-b2ef1fcfa058%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarly%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPriem%20attended%20RPI%20in%20Troy%2C%20New%20York%2C%20graduating%20in%201982%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20computer%20electrical%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20job%20after%20graduating%20from%20RPI%20was%20with%20the%20now-defunct%20tech%20firm%20Vermont%20Microsystems.%20But%20it%20was%20a%20move%20to%20California%20to%20work%20at%20Sun%20Microsystems%20that%20would%20kick%20his%20career%20into%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Sun%2C%20Priem%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20aforementioned%20graphics%20card%2C%20making%20his%20mark%20on%20the%20tech%20world%20and%20establishing%20himself%20as%20a%20leading%20figure%20in%20the%20design%20and%20development%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d827f30c-58c8-4943-ac12-322c2d43dc35%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENvidia's%20founding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20story%20goes%20%E2%80%94%20corroborated%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlXLBTBBil2U%26t%3D30s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanford%20Business%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%20interview%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%20%E2%80%94%20Huang%2C%20Priem%2C%20and%20Nvidia's%20other%20co-founder%2C%20Chris%20Malachowsky%2C%20met%20at%20a%20Silicon%20Valley%20Denny's%20restaurant%20to%20discuss%20their%20potential%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMalachowsky%20worked%20at%20Sun%20Microsystems%20along%20with%20Priem%2C%20while%20Huang%20had%20worked%20at%20both%20LSI%20Logic%20and%20Advanced%20Micro%20Devices.%20And%2C%20famously%2C%20before%20graduating%20from%20Oregon%20State%20University%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20electrical%20engineering%20(he'd%20add%20a%20masters%20from%20Stanford%20in%20the%20same%20field%20later)%2C%20Huang%20worked%20as%20a%20dishwasher%20at%20Denny's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20was%20founded%20on%20April%2015%2C%201993.%20The%20founders%20shared%20a%20%26quot%3Ba%20vision%20to%20bring%203D%20graphics%20to%20the%20gaming%20and%20multimedia%20markets%26quot%3B%20and%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20do%20