Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20draft%20proposal%20presented%20by%20US%20officials%20is%20more%20%26quot%3Bmaximalist%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20original%20version%20floated%20in%20February%2C%20which%20proposed%20Kyiv%20giving%20Washington%20%24500bn%20worth%20of%20rare%20metals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20sources%2C%20the%20report%20said%20the%20new%20document%20has%20several%20%26quot%3BEaster%20eggs%26quot%3B%2C%20one%20of%20them%20being%20the%20Trump%20administration%20demanding%20that%20the%20US%20government's%20International%20Development%20Finance%20Corporation%20take%20control%20of%20a%20natural%20gas%20pipeline%20from%20Russian%20energy%20giant%20Gazprom%20across%20Ukraine%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20America%20Wants%20the%20Deal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20wants%20control%20over%20Ukraine's%20mineral%20deposits%2C%20which%20include%20prized%20rare%20earths%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bpayback%26quot%3B%20in%20return%20for%20weapons%20delivered%20to%20Kyiv%20by%20the%20previous%20Biden%20administration%20after%20the%20start%20Russia-Ukraine%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20has%20repeatedly%20claimed%20that%20America%20has%20given%20Ukraine%20between%20%24300bn%20and%20%24350bn%20in%20aid%2C%20and%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20that%20money%20back%26quot%3B%20through%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20first%20discussed%20the%20proposed%20deal%20with%20Trump%20last%20September%2C%20when%20he%20was%20the%20Republican%20nominee%20for%20the%20Presidential%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20was%20to%20give%20the%20US%20access%20to%20Ukraine's%20underdeveloped%20mineral%20sector.%20The%20Ukrainian%20leader%20envisaged%20a%20deal%20that%20would%20see%20the%20incoming%20Trump%20administration%20supply%20Ukraine%20with%20weapons%2C%20in%20return%20for%20future%20profits%20from%20joint%20investments%2C%20however%2C%20Washington%20has%20made%20no%20clear%20promise%20on%20the%20issue%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENegotiation%20So%20Far%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20and%20Ukrainian%20officials%20met%20on%20Friday%20on%20a%20US%20proposal%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20Ukraine's%20mineral%20wealth.%20But%2C%20the%20prospects%20for%20a%20breakthrough%20were%20scant%20given%20the%20meeting's%20%26quot%3Bantagonistic%26quot%3B%20atmosphere%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strains%20in%20the%20Washington%20talks%20stemmed%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20latest%20draft%20proposal%2C%20which%20is%20more%20expansive%20than%20the%20original%20version%2C%20the%20agency%20reported%2C%20quoting%20a%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20negotiating%20environment%20is%20very%20antagonistic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bmaximalist%26quot%3B%20draft%20submitted%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20was%20confirmed%20by%20a%20Treasury%20Department%20spokesperson%2C%20who%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20in%20nature.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20government%20has%20hired%20law%20firm%20Hogan%20Lovells%20as%20an%20outside%20adviser%20on%20the%20minerals%20deal%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20America's%20New%20Proposal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20draft%20would%20give%20the%20US%20privileged%20access%20to%20Ukraine's%20mineral%20deposits%20and%20require%20Kyiv%20to%20place%20in%20a%20joint%20investment%20fund%20all%20income%20from%20the%20exploitation%20of%20natural%20resources%20by%20Ukrainian%20state%20and%20private%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20deal%2C%20however%2C%20would%20not%20provide%20US%20security%20guarantees%20to%20Kyiv%20-%20a%20top%20priority%20of%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20-%20for%20its%20fight%20against%20Russian%20forces%20occupying%20some%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BEaster%20eggs%26quot%3B%20found%20in%20the%20document%20was%20a%20demand%20that%20the%20US%20government's%20International%20Development%20Finance%20Corporation%20take%20control%20of%20a%20natural%20gas%20pipeline%20that%20runs%20from%20the%20town%20of%20Sudzha%20in%20western%20Russia%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20city%20of%20Uzhhorod%2C%20on%20the%20border%20with%20the%20EU%20and%20Slovakia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20in%20Soviet%20times%2C%20the%20pipeline%20was%20shut%20by%20Ukraine%20on%20January%201%2C%20after%20its%20five-year%20contract%20with%20the%20Russian%20state%20energy%20company%20Gazprom%20expired.%20The%20major%20energy%20route%20has%20earned%20both%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20euros%20in%20transit%20fees%2C%20including%20during%20the%20first%20three%20years%20of%20full-scale%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUkraine%20Refuses%20To%20Back%20Down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20a%20minerals%20deal%20should%20be%20profitable%20for%20both%20countries%20and%20could%20be%20structured%20in%20a%20way%20that%20would%20help%20modernize%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20just%20defending%20what%20belongs%20to%20Ukraine.%20It%20should%20be%20beneficial%20for%20both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Ukraine.%20This%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolodymyr%20Landa%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20with%20the%20Centre%20for%20Economic%20Strategy%2C%20a%20Kyiv%20thinktank%2C%20told%20The%20Guardian%20that%20the%20Americans%20were%20out%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20they%20can%20get%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20predicted%20that%20America's%20bullying%20%26quot%3Bcolonial-type%26quot%3B%20demands%20had%20little%20chance%20of%20being%20accepted%20by%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744529100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F3n5cp4cg_trump-zelensky_625x300_04_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-ukraine-mineral-deal-why-trump-wants-kyiv-to-handover-key-pipeline-carrying-russian-gas-8153454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Trump%20administration%20has%20a%20new%20demand--%20US%20control%20over%20a%20crucial%20pipeline%20passing%20through%20Ukraine%20that's%20used%20to%20send%20Russian%20gas%20to%20Europe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22150%20Arrested%20In%20Bengal%2C%20BJP%20Alleges%20Hindus%20Fleeing%20Home%20After%20Waqf%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMurshidabad%20is%20among%20the%20areas%20in%20Bengal%20that%20have%20erupted%20in%20protest%20after%20the%20Parliament%20passed%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20which%20introduces%20key%20changes%20to%20laws%20governing%20the%20management%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmong%20the%20affected%20areas%20are%20Suti%2C%20Dhulian%2C%20Samserganj%20and%20Jangipur%20areas.%20State%20police%20have%20now%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20under%20control%20and%20prohibitory%20orders%20are%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20large%20gatherings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20ordered%20the%20deployment%20of%20central%20forces%20to%20keep%20the%20peace.%20The%20court%20yesterday%20said%20the%20situation%20is%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20and%20volatile%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BConstitutional%20Courts%20cannot%20be%20a%20mute%20spectator%20and%20embroil%20itself%20in%20technical%20defences%20when%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20people%20are%20at%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20appealed%20for%20calm%20and%20said%20those%20behind%20the%20riots%20were%20harming%20society.%20She%20said%20it%20is%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20not%20the%20state%20government%2C%20that%20has%20brought%20the%20law%20in%20question.%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20reiterated%20that%20her%20party%20does%20not%20support%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESuvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Bengal%20Assembly%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20more%20than%20400%20Hindus%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20flee%20their%20homes.%20%26quot%3BReligious%20persecution%20in%20Bengal%20is%20real.%20Appeasement%20politics%20of%20TMC%20has%20emboldened%20radical%20elements.%20Hindus%20are%20being%20hunted%2C%20our%20people%20are%20running%20for%20their%20lives%20in%20their%20own%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20violent%20and%20welcomed%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20direction.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20has%20stepped%20in%20and%20given%20the%20appropriate%20decision%20at%20the%20appropriate%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EViolence%20in%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20Murshidabad%20district%20began%20on%20April%208%2C%20when%20stones%20were%20thrown%20at%20police%20and%20some%20police%20vehicles%20set%20on%20fire.%20Earlier%2C%20massive%20protests%20were%20held%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20including%20capital%20Kolkata%2C%20against%20the%20new%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWest%20Bengal%20DGP%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20has%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20told%20the%20police%20not%20to%20tolerate%20any%20hooliganism.%20He%20said%20the%20protests%20started%20with%20a%20demonstration%2C%20destruction%20of%20public%20property%20followed%20and%20then%20it%20took%20a%20communal%20angl