Tahawwur%20Rana%20will%20be%20extradited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio's%20office%20dismissed%20Rana's%20lawyer's%20claims%20of%20torture%20and%20said%20that%20sending%20Rana%20to%20India%20followed%20all%20international%20rules%2C%20especially%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20Against%20Torture.%20The%20US%20also%20offered%20to%20pass%20on%20any%20updated%20medical%20records%20to%20Indian%20officials%20to%20help%20them%20prepare%20for%20Rana's%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20with%20the%20issuance%20of%20this%20warrant%2C%20Rana%20may%20be%20surrendered%20to%20India%20at%20any%20time.%20So%20we%20need%20the%20medical%20information%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETahawwur%20Rana%20in%20NIA%20custody%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flove-for-pak-army-uniform-meets-with-isi-day-1-of-tahawwur-rana-probe-8146158%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETahawwur%20Rana%3C%2Fa%3E%20landed%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%20and%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20for%2018%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20the%20anti-terror%20agency%20is%20aiming%20to%20unravel%20the%20role%20of%20a%20man%20that%20Rana%20met%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-ranas-probe-reveals-elusive-dubai-man-who-knew-of-26-11-attacks-8145626%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDubai%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebefore%20the%20attacks%20and%20began%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20renewal%20of%20an%20office%20lease%20in%20Mumbai%20registered%20as%20Rana's%20immigration%20agency.%20The%20office%20was%20reportedly%20used%20as%20a%20cover%20by%2026%2F11%20attacks%20mastermind%20David%20Headley%20to%20conduct%20reccee%20of%20potential%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20collect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2