1080183718695306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2012%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CVisiting%20America%20is%20not%20an%20entitlement.%20It%20is%20a%20privilege%20extended%20to%20those%20who%20respect%20our%20laws%20and%20values.%20And%2C%20as%20Secretary%20of%20State%2C%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rubio%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERubio%2C%20who%20represented%20Florida%20in%20the%20US%20Senate%20from%202011%20to%202025%20before%20assuming%20his%20current%20role%2C%20said%20that%20under%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Nationality%20Act%20(INA)%2C%20%E2%80%9Caliens%E2%80%9D%20who%20promote%20or%20support%20terrorism%20%E2%80%94%20including%20backing%20terrorist%20organisations%20such%20as%20Hamas%20%E2%80%94%20are%20ineligible%20for%20US%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20INA%20gives%20us%20broad%20authority%20to%20revoke%20a%20visa.%20This%20authority%20is%20fundamental%20to%20safeguarding%20our%20national%20security%2C%20as%20well%20as%20protecting%20Americans%20and%20lawful%20visitors%20within%20our%20borders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERubio%20defended%20the%20administration's%20intensified%20scrutiny%20of%20visa%20holders%2C%20noting%20that%20security%20vetting%20is%20an%20ongoing%20process%2C%20even%20after%20a%20visa%20has%20been%20issued.%20%E2%80%9CUS%20visa%20holders%20should%20know%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20the%20US%20government's%20rigorous%20security%20vetting%20does%20not%20end%20once%20a%20visa%20is%20granted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Secretary%20of%20State%20added%20that%20the%20government%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20law%20enforcement%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20continuously%20monitors%20visa%20holders%20to%20identify%20any%20potential%20threats%20or%20violations.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20visas%20may%20be%20revoked%20if%20the%20visa%20holder%20has%20engaged%20in%20violent%20crime%20or%20drunk%20driving%2C%20supporting%20terrorism%2C%20overstaying%20the%20time%20permitted%20for%20their%20visit%2C%20performing%20illegal%20work%20--%20or%20anything%20else%20that%20violates%20the%20terms%20on%20which%20we%20granted%20them%20this%20privilege%20or%20compromises%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20fellow%20Americans%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMarco%20Rubio%20also%20pointed%20to%20recent%20incidents%20following%20the%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20terrorist%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20as%20a%20case%20study%20for%20increased%20vigilance.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20these%20foreign%20student%20visitors%20engaged%20in%20antisemitic%20activities%20and%20intimidation%20of%20Americans%2C%20many%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20of%20the%20Jewish%20faith%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20foreigners%20shut%20down%20college%20campuses%20for%20American%20citizens%2C%20harassed%20Jewish%20students%2C%20blocked%20highways%2C%20and%20stormed%20buildings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20administration%20would%20not%20tolerate%20such%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20committed%20to%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20stop%20these%20activities%20at%20American%20universities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rubio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20the%20legal%20precedent%20for%20the%20government's%20position.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20made%20clear%20for%20decades%20that%20visa%20holders%20or%20other%20aliens%20cannot%20use%20the%20First%20Amendment%20to%20shield%20otherwise%20impermissible%20actions%20taken%20to%20support%20designated%20foreign%20terrorist%20organizations%20like%20Hamas%2C%20Hizballah%2C%20or%20the%20Houthis%2C%20or%20violate%20other%20US%20laws.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20a%20zero-tolerance%20approach%2C%20Rubio%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20am%20Secretary%2C%20we%20will%20never%20hesitate%20to%20act%20decisively%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20close%20coordination%20with%20our%20US%20government%20partners%20%E2%80%93%20when%20information%20indicates%20a%20visa%20holder%20could%20compromise%20our%20security%2C%20has%20violated%20US%20law%2C%20or%20visa%20revocation%20is%20otherwise%20warranted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20concluded%20with%20the%20message%2C%20%E2%80%9CUS%20visas%20are%20a%20privilege%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20right%2C%20reserved%20for%20those%20who%20make%20the%20United%20States%20better%2C%20not%20seek%20to%20destroy%20it%20from%20the%20inside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744520580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Faehc9918_marco-rubio_625x300_13_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftop-us-diplomat-marco-rubio-on-why-they-donald-trump-team-revokes-visas-visiting-america-is-not-an-entitlement-its-a-privilege-8152598%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20coming%20to%20power%20in%20January%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20deported%20some%20foreign%20students%2C%20has%20revoked%20multiple%20visas%20and%20has%20warned%20universities%20of%20federal%20funding%20cuts%20over%20pro-Palestinian%20protests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftop-us-diplomat-marco-rubio-on-why-they-donald-trump-team-revokes-visas-visiting-america-is-not-an-entitlement-its-a-privilege-8152598%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhishek%20Names%20MI%20Star%20Who%20Supported%20Him%20In%20Tough%20Times.%20Not%20Hardik%2C%20Rohit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108562-abhishek-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20rose%20the%20highest%20as%20his%20team%20secured%20a%20ground-breaking%20victory%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20match%20on%20Saturday.%20Abhishek%20was%20utterly%20dominant%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20the%20match%2C%20scoring%20141%20runs%20off%20just%2055%20balls%2C%20to%20take%20the%20team%20home%20with%202%20overs%20to%20spare.%20After%20the%20game%2C%20Abhishek%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20battling%20fever%20over%20the%20last%20four%20days%20but%20continued%20to%20receive%20words%20of%20encouragement%20from%20former%20India%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuvraj%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F456-yuvraj-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuvraj%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20current%20Mumbai%20Indians%20vice-captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20had%20failed%20to%20fire%20runs%20in%20any%20of%20the%205%20matches%20for%20SRH%20until%20the%20game%20against%20PBKS%2C%20breathing%20a%20huge%20sigh%20of%20relief.%20Yuvraj%20has%20been%20a%20mentor%20for%20Abhishek%20for%20a%20long%20time%20while%20Suryakumar%20is%20also%20a%20good%20friend.%20Keeping%20rivalry%20aside%2C%20Surya%20encouraged%20the%20SRH%20batter%20to%20move%20ahead%20of%20poor%20form%20and%20try%20to%20give%20his%20best%20on%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20sick%20for%20four%20days-I%20had%20a%20fever.%20But%20I%20feel%20really%20grateful%20to%20have%20people%20like%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20around%20me.%20They%20kept%20calling%2C%20kept%20checking%20in%2C%20and%20they%20believed%20in%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhishek%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20I%20started%20to%20doubt%20myself%20a%20little%2C%20they%20didn't.%20That%20belief%20from%20people%20like%20them-it%20matters%20a%20lot.%20When%20someone%20like%20that%20believes%20in%20you%2C%20you%20start%20believing%20in%20yourself%20again.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20was%20just%20about%20that%20one%20innings.%20I%20was%20waiting%20for%20it.%20And%20today%20it%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhishek%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20game%2C%20Abhishek%20had%20only%20scored%2051%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2010.50.%20He%20admitted%20in%20the%20media%20conference%20that%20there%20was%20pressure%20on%20him%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20-%20if%20I%20say%20there%20wasn't%2C%20I'd%20be%20lying.%20When%20you%20don't%20perform%20well%20for%20three%20or%20four%20innings%2C%20and%20the%20team%20loses%2C%20the%20pressure%20does%20build%20up%20on%20individual%20players.%20But%20like%20I%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20ceremony%2C%20I%20never%20felt%20any%20negativity%20in%20the%20team.%20No%20one%20had%20the%20mindset%20of%20'we're%20losing.'%20Everyone%20stayed%20positive%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhishek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20knew%20something%20big%20was%20coming%20from%20the%20team-and%20luckily%2C%20we%20got%20to%20break%20that%20four-match%20losing%20streak%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20southpaw%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744520460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fjrsk1ne8_abhishek-sharma-bcci_625x300_13_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fabhishek-sharma-reveals-how-mi-star-encouraged-him-after-repeated-failures-its-not-rohit-or-hardik-8152701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhishek%20Sharma%20thanked%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20and%20a%20special%20Mumbai%20Indians%20star%20after%20his%2055-ball%20141%20against%20Punjab%20Kings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonical