Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FByvdpRw4nMA%3Fsi%3DGdOmGtAyfjsgXeM6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20integrating%20solar%20systems%20(in%20some%20cases)%20to%20harness%20green%20power%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20the%20forest%20grid-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20is%20the%20excavation%20stage%20where%20the%20land%20is%20prepared%20for%20plantation.%20Its%20productivity%20is%20enhanced%20with%20cow%20dung%20and%20rice%20husks%3B%20the%20latter%20is%20a%20dense%20source%20of%20carbon%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20water%20and%20nutrient-holding%20capacity%20of%20the%20soil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soil%20is%20mulched%20with%20agro-waste%20and%20then%20nourished%20with%20manure%20and%20vermicompost%2C%20which%20boost%20its%20nutrition%20quotient.%20What%20follows%20is%20the%20plantation%20activity.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20forest%20created%20by%20CATCH%20Foundation%20is%20a%20green%20oasis%20around%20which%20civilisation%20thrives.%20The%20foundation%20wishes%20to%20make%20forests%20mainstays%20in%20cities%20rather%20than%20fleeting%20inclusions.%20To%20ensure%20this%20permanence%2C%20there%20is%20a%20stringent%20assessment%20of%20these%20forests%20during%20the%20first%20three%20years.%20One%20of%20the%20main%20aims%20during%20this%20time%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20forest%20weed-free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Catch%20Foundation%20does%20a%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20f